<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Document</title>
</head>
<body>
  <!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>記憶の継承 — 体験化プロジェクト</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+JP:wght@300;400;600&family=Shippori+Mincho:wght@400;500;700&family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;1,300;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --ink: #1a1510;
    --sepia: #c8b89a;
    --aged: #e8dfc8;
    --bone: #f4f0e8;
    --rust: #8b3a2a;
    --muted: #6b5f52;
    --ghost: rgba(200,184,154,0.15);
    --paper: #faf7f2;
  }

  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background: var(--paper);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
    overflow-x: hidden;
    cursor: none;
  }

  /* Custom cursor */
  .cursor {
    position: fixed;
    width: 10px; height: 10px;
    background: var(--rust);
    border-radius: 50%;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 9999;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    transition: transform 0.1s ease, width 0.3s ease, height 0.3s ease, opacity 0.3s ease;
    mix-blend-mode: multiply;
  }

  .cursor-ring {
    position: fixed;
    width: 36px; height: 36px;
    border: 1px solid var(--sepia);
    border-radius: 50%;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 9998;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    transition: transform 0.15s ease, width 0.3s, height 0.3s, opacity 0.3s;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  /* Grain overlay */
  body::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)' opacity='0.04'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 9990;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  /* Page line decorations */
  .line-h {
    width: 100%;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--sepia), transparent);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  /* ─── HERO ─── */
  #hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-rows: 1fr auto;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 0 6vw;
  }

  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 60% 40%, rgba(139,58,42,0.06) 0%, transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 50% at 20% 80%, rgba(200,184,154,0.12) 0%, transparent 50%);
  }

  .hero-year {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(160px, 28vw, 360px);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: transparent;
    -webkit-text-stroke: 1px rgba(200,184,154,0.3);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    white-space: nowrap;
    user-select: none;
    pointer-events: none;
    animation: yearFade 2s ease forwards;
    opacity: 0;
  }

  @keyframes yearFade {
    to { opacity: 1; }
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding-top: 18vh;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(11px, 1.2vw, 14px);
    font-style: italic;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: slideUp 1s 0.3s ease forwards;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-family: 'Shippori Mincho', serif;
    font-size: clamp(42px, 7vw, 96px);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: slideUp 1s 0.5s ease forwards;
  }

  .hero-title em {
    font-style: normal;
    color: var(--rust);
    position: relative;
  }

  .hero-title em::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 2px;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--rust);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: clamp(13px, 1.4vw, 17px);
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 2;
    max-width: 480px;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: slideUp 1s 0.7s ease forwards;
  }

  .hero-scroll {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    color: var(--muted);
    opacity: 0;
    animation: slideUp 1s 1s ease forwards;
  }

  .scroll-line {
    width: 60px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--sepia);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .scroll-line::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: -100%;
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    background: var(--rust);
    animation: scanLine 2s 1.5s ease infinite;
  }

  @keyframes scanLine {
    0% { left: -100%; }
    50% { left: 100%; }
    100% { left: 100%; }
  }

  .hero-nav {
    position: absolute;
    top: 3rem;
    right: 6vw;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--muted);
    z-index: 10;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeIn 1s 1.2s ease forwards;
  }

  .hero-nav a {
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }

  .hero-nav a:hover { color: var(--rust); }

  .hero-logo {
    position: absolute;
    top: 3rem;
    left: 6vw;
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    color: var(--muted);
    z-index: 10;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeIn 1s 1.2s ease forwards;
  }

  .hero-bottom {
    padding-bottom: 3rem;
    z-index: 2;
    position: relative;
  }

  @keyframes slideUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  @keyframes fadeIn {
    to { opacity: 1; }
  }

  /* ─── SECTION BASE ─── */
  section {
    padding: clamp(80px, 12vh, 140px) 6vw;
    position: relative;
  }

  .section-label {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-style: italic;
    letter-spacing: 0.35em;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-num {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(72px, 12vw, 140px);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: transparent;
    -webkit-text-stroke: 1px rgba(200,184,154,0.4);
    position: absolute;
    top: -0.3em;
    right: 6vw;
    line-height: 1;
    user-select: none;
  }

  /* ─── PROBLEM ─── */
  #problem {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--bone);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  #problem .section-num {
    -webkit-text-stroke: 1px rgba(200,184,154,0.15);
  }

  .problem-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 6vw;
    align-items: start;
    margin-top: 4rem;
  }

  .problem-statement {
    font-family: 'Shippori Mincho', serif;
    font-size: clamp(26px, 3.5vw, 48px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.6;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }

  .problem-statement strong {
    color: var(--sepia);
  }

  .problem-detail {
    padding-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .problem-detail p {
    font-size: clamp(13px, 1.3vw, 16px);
    line-height: 2.2;
    color: rgba(232,223,200,0.7);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .counter-group {
    display: flex;
    gap: 3rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .counter-item .num {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(40px, 5vw, 64px);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--sepia);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .counter-item .label {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    color: rgba(200,184,154,0.6);
    margin-top: 0.4rem;
  }

  /* ─── CONCEPT ─── */
  #concept {
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .concept-intro {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
    gap: 5vw;
    align-items: start;
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  .concept-lead {
    font-family: 'Shippori Mincho', serif;
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 56px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.4;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }

  .concept-desc {
    padding-top: 1rem;
    font-size: clamp(13px, 1.3vw, 16px);
    line-height: 2.3;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .pillars {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2px;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .pillar {
    background: var(--aged);
    padding: clamp(28px, 3vw, 48px);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: background 0.4s;
  }

  .pillar:hover { background: var(--sepia); }

  .pillar::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0; left: 0;
    width: 100%; height: 3px;
    background: var(--rust);
    transform: scaleX(0);
    transform-origin: left;
    transition: transform 0.4s ease;
  }

  .pillar:hover::before { transform: scaleX(1); }

  .pillar-num {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-style: italic;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .pillar-title {
    font-family: 'Shippori Mincho', serif;
    font-size: clamp(20px, 2vw, 28px);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .pillar-text {
    font-size: clamp(12px, 1.1vw, 14px);
    line-height: 2;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  /* ─── CONTENT / EXPERIENCE ─── */
  #experience {
    background: #f0ebe0;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .exp-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 5rem);
    margin-top: 4rem;
  }

  .exp-card {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .exp-card-inner {
    background: var(--paper);
    padding: clamp(28px, 3vw, 48px);
    height: 100%;
    border-top: 3px solid transparent;
    transition: border-color 0.4s;
    position: relative;
  }

  .exp-card:hover .exp-card-inner {
    border-color: var(--rust);
  }

  .exp-type {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-style: italic;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .exp-title {
    font-family: 'Shippori Mincho', serif;
    font-size: clamp(22px, 2.5vw, 34px);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .exp-body {
    font-size: clamp(13px, 1.2vw, 15px);
    line-height: 2.2;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .exp-visual {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(200,184,154,0.4);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(13px, 1.3vw, 16px);
    color: var(--muted);
    position: relative;
    background: var(--aged);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* Fake SNS post */
  .sns-post {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
    font-style: normal;
  }

  .sns-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }

  .sns-avatar {
    width: 32px; height: 32px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--sepia);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-style: normal;
    color: var(--ink);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .sns-name {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .sns-date {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .sns-text {
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .sns-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--rust);
    margin-right: 0.5rem;
  }

  /* ─── STORY ─── */
  #story {
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .story-wrap {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 6vw;
    align-items: center;
    margin-top: 4rem;
  }

  .story-text {
    font-family: 'Shippori Mincho', serif;
    font-size: clamp(20px, 2.5vw, 32px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 2;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .story-text p + p {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .story-text .accent {
    color: var(--rust);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .story-aside {
    border-left: 2px solid var(--sepia);
    padding-left: 3rem;
  }

  .story-quote {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(36px, 4vw, 52px);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .story-quote span {
    color: var(--rust);
  }

  .effects-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .effects-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(200,184,154,0.3);
    font-size: clamp(13px, 1.2vw, 15px);
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .effects-list li::before {
    content: '—';
    color: var(--rust);
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 0.1rem;
  }

  /* ─── CTA ─── */
  #cta {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--bone);
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 60vh;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .cta-bg-text {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(80px, 18vw, 220px);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-style: italic;
    color: transparent;
    -webkit-text-stroke: 1px rgba(200,184,154,0.08);
    white-space: nowrap;
    user-select: none;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .cta-label {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-style: italic;
    letter-spacing: 0.35em;
    color: var(--sepia);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .cta-headline {
    font-family: 'Shippori Mincho', serif;
    font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 64px);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .cta-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.2rem;
    padding: 1.2rem 3rem;
    background: transparent;
    border: 1px solid var(--sepia);
    color: var(--bone);
    font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    cursor: none;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: color 0.4s;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .cta-btn::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: var(--rust);
    transform: translateX(-101%);
    transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.7,0,0.3,1);
  }

  .cta-btn:hover::before { transform: translateX(0); }

  .cta-btn span {
    position: relative;
  }

  .cta-btn-arrow {
    position: relative;
    width: 24px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--sepia);
    transition: width 0.3s;
  }

  .cta-btn-arrow::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    right: 0;
    top: -3px;
    width: 7px; height: 7px;
    border-right: 1px solid var(--sepia);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--sepia);
    transform: rotate(45deg);
  }

  .cta-btn:hover .cta-btn-arrow { width: 40px; }

  /* ─── FOOTER ─── */
  footer {
    padding: 3rem 6vw;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(200,184,154,0.2);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  /* ─── SCROLL REVEAL ─── */
  .reveal {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    transition: opacity 0.9s ease, transform 0.9s ease;
  }

  .reveal.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  .reveal-delay-1 { transition-delay: 0.1s; }
  .reveal-delay-2 { transition-delay: 0.2s; }
  .reveal-delay-3 { transition-delay: 0.35s; }
  .reveal-delay-4 { transition-delay: 0.5s; }

  /* ─── PROGRESS BAR ─── */
  .progress-bar {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--rust);
    z-index: 9997;
    transition: width 0.1s;
    transform-origin: left;
  }

  /* ─── RESPONSIVE ─── */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .problem-grid,
    .concept-intro,
    .exp-grid,
    .story-wrap {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .pillars { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }

    .counter-group { gap: 2rem; }

    .hero-nav { display: none; }

    .section-num { display: none; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="cursor" id="cursor"></div>
<div class="cursor-ring" id="cursorRing"></div>
<div class="progress-bar" id="progressBar"></div>

<!-- ─── HERO ─── -->
<section id="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-year">1945</div>

  <div class="hero-logo">MEMORY PROJECT</div>
  <nav class="hero-nav">
    <a href="#problem">問題提起</a>
    <a href="#concept">コンセプト</a>
    <a href="#experience">活動</a>
    <a href="#cta">参加する</a>
  </nav>

  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">記憶の継承プロジェクト — 87 ハチナナ
    </div>
    <h1 class="hero-title">
      80年前の出来事を<br>
      「資料」から<br>
      <em>「体験」へ</em>
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-subtitle">
      戦争の記憶は、時間とともに遠ざかっていく。<br>
      だからこそ今、私たちは「感じる」形で残したい。
    </p>
    <div class="hero-scroll">
      <div class="scroll-line"></div>
      <span>scroll</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-bottom">
    <div class="line-h"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ─── PROBLEM ─── -->
<section id="problem">
  <div class="section-num">01</div>
  <div class="section-label reveal">問題提起 — Problem</div>

  <div class="problem-grid">
    <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1">
      <p class="problem-statement">
        語り部は、<br>
        <strong>年々減っている。</strong><br>
        直接話を聞く機会も、<br>
        確実に失われている。
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="problem-detail reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <p>
        多くの人が戦争を「知っている」。<br>
        でも、それは本当に"実感"できているだろうか。
      </p>
      <p>
        知識として持っていても、<br>
        体の中に響かない。心に届かない。<br>
        そのままでは、記憶は数字になる。
      </p>

      <div class="counter-group">
        <div class="counter-item reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <div class="num" data-target="80">0</div>
          <div class="label">年が経過した</div>
        </div>
        
